A '''Cathorn''' was a creature bio-constructed from a feline animal of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Charon/Legends|Charon]]. It exhibited armor-like hide, and had the spiked tail of an [[Ithorian Barbed Flyer]] grafted to its body. It was capable of leaping long distances.

